Before yesterday, I had never been to a Panda Express. I was in the mood for Chinese food so I chose to eat there. To be frank, I was very impressed with the food and service. The Peking Pork was my favorite part of the meal. The service was very fast as well. I got in and out of the line in about three minutes and the line was rather long. Overall, they have achieved a good balance of good food and speedy service. I will definitely return to Panda Express in the future.
